<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h2">Discussion / Conversation Data Space</bridgehead>
<para>Each Wiki, Weblog, Feed Manager, Bookmark Manager, Mail, and Photo Gallery, application instance with &quot;Conversation&quot; functionality enabled results in the generation of SIOC instance data from the ODS Discussion Application.
 For example, in the Weblog Data Space this implies that all comments are delegated to the Discussion Data Space application (which is an application of Virtuoso&#39;s NNTP engine) and exposed as SIOC data automatically.</para>
<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h3">Key ODS-Discussion to SIOC Mappings</bridgehead>

